Mexico PRI Files Claim Against Calderon For Drug Gangs Comments

-- B y   N a c h a   C a t t a n
-- 
2011-10-18T20:02:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/mexico-pri-files-claim-against-calderon-for-drug-gangs-comments.html
Mexico ’s main opposition party
filed a complaint against President Felipe Calderon before the
electoral institute claiming he wrongfully interfered with next
year’s presidential election.  The  Institutional Revolutionary Party , as the political
party is known, filed the complaint today in Mexico City, after
Calderon said that some members of the party believe “deals”
of the past with organized crime would work today.  Calderon made his comments in an interview with The New
York Times published Oct. 15.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Nacha Cattan in Mexico City at 
 ncattan@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jose Enrique Arrioja at 
 jarrioja@bloomberg.net  